                    <ul>
                        <li>Notification Settings</li>
                        <li>Auto password protection</li>
                        <li>Kinky and Vanilla version (separate Apps)</li>
                    </ul>

            <p/>v1.4<br/>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Picture upload</li>
                        <li>Timestamp field for Notification History Items</li>
                        <li>Clear All menu option for Notification History</li>
                    </ul>

            <p/>v1.3<br/>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Receive broader set of Notification</li>
                        <li>View your Notification History</li>
                        <li>Get information about new features at about screen</li>
                        <li>Use hardware menu button for opening the menu</li>
                    </ul>

            <p/>v1.2<br/>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Share your profile with others via NFC beam</li>
                        <li>Accept shared profiles and create a new friend request at Friend Requests screen</li>
                    </ul>

            <p/>v1.1<br/>
                    <ul>
                        <li>View your list of incoming, pending friend requests</li>
                        <li>Approve or Reject your pending friend requests</li>
                    </ul>

            <p/>v1.0<br/>
